pullRequest.body:
Changing `Matrix.row` and `Matrix.col` to use arbitrary `Unique` type for indexing the single column/row.

---

Compare to #11522, which presents a simpler possible solution.

For more details, see the other PR.

[Zulip discussion](https://leanprover.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/287929-mathlib4/topic/Why.20does.20.60Matrix.2Erow.60.20use.20.20.60Unit.60.20instead.20of.20.60Fin.201.60.3F)
